    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#mohamed-jmr-cdl2007"/>, pp. 38-39, n. <citedRange>5</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>57.2007, B</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>108900</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#cdl1998b"/>, pp. <citedRange>411-412</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>48.2059 b</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2020a"/>, p. <citedRange>188-189</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
              </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Ἀκέσανδρος"><unclear>Ἀ</unclear>κέσανδρον</name> 
                        <space quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
                        <persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Θεύχρηστος" type="patronymic">Θεοχρήστω</name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Ἀκέσανδρος"><supplied reason="lost">Ἀ</supplied><unclear>κ</unclear>έσανδρος</name> 
                        <space quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
                        <persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Τίμαρχος" type="patronymic">Τιμάρχω</name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/>τὸν <w lemma="ἄμναμμος">ἄμναμμον</w>
                 
                </ab></div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Akésandros fils de Timarkhos <supplied reason="subaudible">a consacré la statue d'</supplied>Akésandros fils de Théokhrestos son petit-fils.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Akesandros son of Timarchos <supplied reason="subaudible">dedicated the statue of</supplied> Akesandros son of Theochrestos his grandson.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Akesandros figlio di Timarchos <supplied reason="subaudible">ha dedicato la statua di</supplied> Akesandros figlio di Theochrestos, suo nipote.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>On the typically Cyrenaean word <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἄμναμμος</foreign> 'grandson', see <bibl><ptr target="#cdl1998b"/>,
                    pp. <citedRange>411-412</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
             <p>A Timarchos son of Akesandros, ephebe in year 3/4 AD (see <ref type="inscription" target="https://ircyr2020.inslib.kcl.ac.uk/en/inscriptions/C.130.html">IRCyr2020 C.130</ref>, ii.40) was probably a descendant of 
                    the present dedicant.</p>
            </div></body>
    </text>
